g.text: Dissolve ingredients (except carbonate, vitamins and sulfide), sparge medium with 100% N2 gas for 30 - 45 min to make it anoxic. Dispense medium under same gas atmosphere into anoxic Hungate-type tubes or serum vials. After autoclaving complete the medium by adding vitamins and sulfide from separately sterilized anoxic stock solutions prepared under 100% N2 gas and carbonate from a sterile anoxic stock solution prepared under 80% N2 and 20% CO2 gas atmosphere. Vitamins are sterilized by filtration. Adjust pH of the complete medium to 7.0-7.2, if necessary.
